        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false },
        "content": "## MinIO Troubleshooting\n\n**Common Issues:**\n\n1. **Connection Refused**: Check if MinIO pod is running\n2. **Access Denied**: Verify credentials in secrets\n3. **Bucket Not Found**: Initialize buckets with `make init-minio`\n4. **Slow Uploads**: Check available storage and memory\n\n**Useful Commands:**\n```bash\n# View MinIO logs\nkubectl logs -n ldp -l app=minio\n\n# Access MinIO Console\nmake minio-forward\n# Open http://localhost:9001\n# Default: admin / minioadmin\n\n# List buckets (using mc client)\nkubectl exec -n ldp minio-0 -- mc ls local/\n\n# Initialize buckets\nmake init-minio\n\n# Check bucket contents\nkubectl exec -n ldp minio-0 -- mc ls local/raw-data/\n```\n\n**Environment Variables:**\n- `MINIO_ROOT_USER`: Admin username\n- `MINIO_ROOT_PASSWORD`: Admin password\n- `MINIO_ENDPOINT`: http://minio:9000",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.1.0",
      "title": "Troubleshooting Tips",
